      "question": "下列何種情況不需要投與抗生素治療?",
      "options": {
        "A": "持續性感染(persistent infection)",
        "B": "蜂窩性組織炎(cellulitis)",
        "C": "骨髓炎(osteomyelitis)",
        "D": "慢性根尖膿腫(chronic apical abscess)"
      },
      "answer": "D"
    },
