      "question": "對於可撤式局部義齒環周牙鈎(circumferential clasp)的敘述,下列何者正確?1鄰接小連接體(proximal minor connector)提供穩定(stabilization)功能 2鄰接板(proximal plate)提供抗衡(reciprocation)功能 3咬合鈎靠(occlusal rest)提供支持(support)功能 4頰側固位牙鈎臂(buccal retentive clasp arm)的剛硬 部分(rigid portion),可提供抗衡(reciprocation)功能",
      "options": {
        "A": "13",
        "B": "24",
        "C": "23",
        "D": "14"
      },
      "answer": "A"
