        "B": "斯皮爾曼等級相關係數(Spearman rank correlation coefficient)",
        "C": "皮爾森相關係數(Pearson correlation coefficient)",
        "D": "雙樣本 t 檢定(2-sample t test)"
      },
      "answer": "B"
    },
